<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: 1.5cm 2cm; }
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #111; line-height: 1.4; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    h1 { font-size: 14pt; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 6px 0 2px 0; color: #1e3a5f; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 8px 0 12px 0; }
    .ref-line { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #888; }
    .lbl { font-size: 8pt; color: #777; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .pname { font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; }
    .pdetail { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #444; }
    .due-box { background: #fff7ed; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; padding: 6px 10px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .sec { font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-left: 3px solid #1e3a5f; padding-left: 6px; margin: 10px 0 4px 0; }
    .amt td { padding: 3px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 9.5pt; }
    .amt td.r { text-align: right; }
    .amt tr.tot td { font-weight: bold; background: #eef2f7; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; }
    .legal { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #aaa; margin-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; padding-top: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <table>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>LeComptoirImmo</strong> — Gestion locative</td>
      <td style="text-align:right;" class="ref-line">
        Réf.&nbsp;{{ avis.id | string | truncate(8, end='') }}
        &nbsp;|&nbsp;{{ avis.created_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}
        {% if avis.status == 'acquitte' %}&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong style="color:#16a34a;">Acquitté</strong>
        {% elif avis.status == 'envoye' %}&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong style="color:#2563eb;">Envoyé</strong>
        {% else %}&nbsp;|&nbsp;Brouillon{% endif %}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h1>Avis d'échéance</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">{{ avis.period_label }}</p>
  <hr>

  <table style="margin-bottom:10px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:50%; vertical-align:top; padding-right:12px; border-right:1px solid #ddd;">
        <div class="lbl">Bailleur / Gestionnaire</div>
        {% if property %}
        <div class="pname">{{ property.name }}</div>
        <div class="pdetail">{{ property.full_address }}</div>
        {% if property.owner_name %}<div class="pdetail">Propriétaire : {{ property.owner_name }}</div>{% endif %}
        {% else %}
        <div class="pname">—</div>
        {% endif %}
      </td>
      <td style="width:50%; vertical-align:top; padding-left:12px;">
        <div class="lbl">Locataire</div>
        <div class="pname">{{ avis.tenant.full_name if avis.tenant else '—' }}</div>
        <div class="pdetail">
          Logement : {{ avis.unit.unit_ref if avis.unit else '—' }}
          {% if property %} — {{ property.full_address }}{% endif %}
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="due-box">
    Loyer à régler avant le : <strong>{{ avis.due_date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}</strong>
    {% if avis.lease and avis.lease.payment_method %}
    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;{% if avis.lease.payment_method == 'virement' %}Virement bancaire
    {% elif avis.lease.payment_method == 'cheque' %}Chèque
    {% elif avis.lease.payment_method == 'prelevement' %}Prélèvement automatique
    {% else %}Espèces{% endif %}
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="sec">Détail de l'appel de loyer</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>Loyer hors charges</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_rent|float) }} €</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Provisions sur charges</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_charges|float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% if avis.amount_apl %}
    <tr><td>Déduction APL (tiers-payant CAF)</td><td class="r">- {{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_apl|float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr class="tot"><td>Total à payer</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_total|float) }} €</td></tr>
  </table>

  {% if avis.notes %}
  <p style="font-size:9pt; margin-top:8px; color:#444;">{{ avis.notes }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="legal">
    Cet avis d'échéance est établi conformément aux dispositions du bail en vigueur. Il ne constitue pas une quittance de loyer.
    La quittance vous sera remise après encaissement du paiement. Document généré par LeComptoirImmo.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
